lyrics:
[Verse]
In shadows deep, where sorrow resides
Death's icy grip, a haunting guide
Lost souls weep, through eternal night
Embrace the dark, devoid of light

[Chorus]
Grim Reaper's call, echoes in the air
Doomed to wander, a life stripped bare
Through the abyss, our spirits fall
Death's cold embrace, claims us all
